               <p>Q. Do you know the prisoner at the bar? - Yes; he was a <rs id="t17921215-8-deflabel40" type="occupation">covenant servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17921215-8-defend116 t17921215-8-deflabel40"></join>. He lived with me four years last November.</p>
               <p>Q. Did he leave you? - He did, on the 9th of October.</p>
               <p>Q. Did he give you any notice he was going to quit you? - None.</p>
               <p>Q. Are you acquainted with his character, and hand-writing? - Yes; I have very frequently seen it.</p>
               <p>Q. Look at that hand-writing; 
